org.hibernate.ogm.util.impl

Annotation Type EffectivelyFinal


  • @Retention(value=SOURCE)
 @Target(value=FIELD)
public @interface EffectivelyFinal
    Documents that a non-final field is only ever modified during the bootstrapping phase, making it effectively final for the remainder of its lifecycle. The annotated field thus may be considered as safely published to other threads.
    Author:
    Gunnar Morling
